<br>
However I think that even a lot of people who claim they are &quot;noble&quot; for using NBG are waiting for the karmic cycle to turn. It's like giving presents at christmas just so you can receive.<br>
<br>
I think FFA is fair but having read your post sometimes it's not morally right. Sometimes someone really really needs an item and deserves it and has terrible luck. I can't stop that. FFA can't stop that. NBG can't stop that whilst its being abused.<br>
<br>
